      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BAREFOOT ZULU (3) has a terrific record this trip with two wins and two placings from four starts. Hit the frame latest (34.80) when second at this track in a Grade 4/5. Looks well placed and should feature. AYDEN'S WARRIOR (8) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (34.62) at Sandown. Form at the trip sound including eight wins. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Bold showing expected. ELITE ONE (1) was in the money again last time and not beaten far when third (38.05) at Bendigo in a Special conditions H. Can hit the frame this time. NIGEL DEVERE (7) won by a wide margin last start. Hard to beat again.",
